		</div>
		<div class="swiper-slide step-slide">
			<div class="slide-layout">
				<div class="img-steps">
					<img src="assets/img/htp-4.png" alt="htp-4">
				</div>
				<p class="py-3 how-to-play-text">Collect as many as you can. If you have the highest number of a single object by end of the week, you’ll win RM338 worth of GrabPay credits!</p>
